=Description=

"Juho Makkonen is a long time collaborative economy enthusiast and Helsinki connector of global collaborative economy network OuiShare. 

He currently serves as the CEO and Co-Founder of a Helsinki-based company Sharetribe. 

Sharetribe has created an open source software product that makes it easy for platform co-ops, cities or aspiring entrepreneurs to create their own peer-to-peer or labour marketplace, in the spirit of Airbnb or Uber, in one day, without technical skills. 

Sharetribe is used by more than 600 companies, non-profits or other organisations in 50 countries."


